quagga.input.subject: Schultes finally Ends
quagga.input.body:
Richard, here is the eighth and final day of Schultes' deposition--Monday, 
August 7--Michael Tomaino, McDonald's lawyer, did all of the questioning.

The next major event is Stickler's deposition starting on September 25th. 

Steve 

 <<Schultes 8.07.txt>>
